<p>
    <h1>PC related:</h1>
    <ul>
        <li>Computer tower + Monitor / laptop / console + monitor(PCs MUST be secured in a case)</li>
        <li>Headset / headphones + microphone</li>
        <li>Mouse, mousemat and Keyboard (and spare batteries/charging cable if wireless!)</li>
