</p>

<p>
    <h1>Comfort:</h1>
    <ul>
        <li>Jumper / hoodie / something warm for night time</li>
        <li>Pillow and sleeping bag/duvet for sleeping + air bed if you are feeling luxurious</li>
        <li>Toothbrush , toothpaste and Deodorant (for everyone's benefit!)</li>
        <li>Wash kit and towel for the morning "freshen up"</li>
        <li>A change of clothes</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<p>
    <h1>Staying alive:</h1>
    <ul>
        <li>Money for pizza order/tuck shop/hotdogs</li>
        <li>A 500ml bottle for filling up with water for rehydration/plenty of other fluids</li>
        <li>Your favourite mug to stock up on tea and coffee with</li>
        <li>Easy access snacks for mid-game re-fueling like crisps, biscuits and chocolate!</li>
        <li>Breakfast bars and/or fruit for the morning "pick me up" and health</li>
        <li>Gifts and sacrifices for the committee</li>
    </ul>
</p>

